column5: How do you like my new painting project I'm workin on?---not exactly stretched canvas but it'll do  Just have it underpainted now---only beaned my noodle on a brow tyne once...  With a rack this nice that paintin better be darn good...  Peace  Bush Guy
Yea little Freudian slip---I'm gettin better though---May have to leave my local chapter of the PPASS Though  (Preverted Painters & Anglers Secret Society)  Bushart
very cool guy. I have seen some nice painting done on racks. Look forward to the finshed product.
id buy that, and i havent even seen the finished product!  cant wait to see what you thro on there.
Oh and btw,dont call me MR.ok MR?LOL
Surely I can Call you Mister--But I won't call you Shirley.  That Pic has to be up to the standards of one like this I've done in the past..  Bushy
